**Privacy Policy**

**Effective Date:** 01-01-2025

**Time Assistant** ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application ("App").

### **1. Information We Collect**
We do not collect any personal information such as your name, email, or contact details. However, the App may store data locally on your device, including:
- Task and Reminder Data (to-do lists, scheduled reminders, and interval reminders)
- Timetable Sessions
- Notification Preferences

### **2. How We Use Your Information**
We use the locally stored data solely to provide the core functionalities of the App, such as managing your tasks, reminders, and schedules. We do not share, sell, or distribute any personal data to third parties.

### **3. Data Storage and Security**
- All data is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to external servers.
- The App does not use cloud storage, ensuring that only you have access to your data.
- Uninstalling the App will delete all stored data.

### **4. Third-Party Services**
The App uses third-party service such as Google AdMob (if applicable). This service may collect anonymous usage data. Please review their respective privacy policies:
- [Google AdMob Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

### **5. Your Rights**
You have the right to:
- Delete your stored data at any time by uninstalling the App.
- Disable notifications through your device settings.

### **6. Changes to This Privacy Policy**
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the App or on our official website (if applicable). We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

### **7. Contact Us**
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
chat.binmotion@gmail.com

By using **Time Assistant**, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
